   members, up to unit-associates, with the
   same multiplicity, up to unit-associates."
  (if (consp lst1)
      (and (member-unit-associate (car lst1) lst2)
	   (bag-equal-unit-associates (cdr lst1)
				      (delete-one-unit-associate (car lst1) 
								 lst2)))
      (atom lst2)))

